      <div class="msgContentFrame">I'm looking to craft some fang arrows for my archer, but I can't find any bats!  I have spent hours running around looking in caves, checking everywhere at night, looking in mines... but I can't find any! Does anyone know where I can find some bats so I can grab their fangs and make some arrowheads?</div>
