      <div class="msgContentFrame">Bats are somewhat rare spawns in cave, you need to kill mobs until they spawn. <br />2 caves I'm sure I have had bats spawned are: <br /> <br />- east of gridania (where the lvl 1 mining leve takes place), in a cave full of mole and fireflay, good spot to farm (and always packed) <br />- a bit north of limsa (close to the first camp on the NW of it) where you have ton of moles outdoor. there are 2 caves, 1 is full of rats (it's not here) and another is full of moles and jellyfish. Bats can spawn here, just kill stuff until they spawn, <br /> <br />Fang are not a partiularly rare drop, but still not common and since bats seldom spawns... <br />I'm sure they are better places but I know of none atm.</div>
