      <div class="msgContentFrame">Mob variety overall seems to be buggy.  I can think of very few areas where night time mobs (fireflies, bats, etc) spawn consistently. And caves, as someone mentioned, only spawn bats maybe 1 in 10. <br /> <br />Some daytime mobs have this problem as well. Marmots seem to be placeholders for anything from beetles, spiders, and dodos. I've even seen crabs respawn as squirrels. <br /> <br /></div>
